= LamportsFactory Typst Sample

This document is a minimal Typst sample for the Typst backend.

== Live preview

Edit this file and rebuild events should update the browser preview.

日本語の表示確認です。Typst backend では `typst compile` により PDF を生成します。

== Formula

$ sum_(i=1)^n i = (n(n + 1)) / 2 $

== List

- LaTeX image uses TeX Live.
- Typst image uses the Typst binary.
- The browser preview remains PDF.js based in both modes.
